# LiveStatsManager

LiveStatsManager is the software that powers [Drexel Dragons](https://drexeldragons.com) basketball TV broadcasts.
It provides APIs for hydrating graphics with the following data:
- Daktronics RTD (Real Time Data) clock and score
- NCAA LiveStats feed for boxscore
- Team and player stats from ESPN
- Locally-stored team metadata (colors, logos, etc.)

## Building from source

`dotnet build`

## Usage

- Configure settings in `appsettings.json`
- Run the application (`LiveStatsManager.exe`)

